Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx80\fscy80\t(0,150,\fscx100\fscy100)}AM I GOING TO HEAVEN?\nDialogue: 0,0:00:02.22,0:00:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx80\fscy80\t(0,150,\fscx100\fscy100)}NO. THEN AM I GOING TO HELL?\nDialogue: 0,0:00:04.55,0:00:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx80\fscy80\t(0,150,\fscx100\fscy100)}NO!\nDialogue: 0,0:00:05.76,0:00:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx80\fscy80\t(0,150,\fscx100\fscy100)}YOU DIE BEFORE YOUR TIME!\nDialogue: 0,0:00:08.07,0:00:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx80\fscy80\t(0,150,\fscx100\fscy100)}SO WHAT DO I DO?\nDialogue: 0,0:00:09.93,0:00:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx80\fscy80\t(0,150,\fscx100\fscy100)}YOU HAVE 24 HOURS TO DO FOUR GOOD DEEDS.\nDialogue: 0,0:00:13.10,0:00:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx80\fscy80\t(0,150,\fscx100\fscy100)}OR YOU'LL GO TO HELL.\nDialogue: 0,0:00:15.07,0:00:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx80\fscy80\t(0,150,\fscx100\fscy100)}I WAS REBORN IN THE MIDDLE OF THIS FOREST, AND...\nDialogue: 0,0:00:18.68,0:00:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx80\fscy80\t(0,150,\fscx100\fscy100)}OH, HELL.\nDialogue: 0,0:00:20.25,0:00:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx80\fscy80\t(0,150,\fscx100\fscy100)}WHO'S SCREAMING?\nDialogue: 0,0:00:22.07,0:00:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx80\fscy80\t(0,150,\fscx100\fscy100)}PLEASE!\nDialogue: 0,0:00:23.45,0:00:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx80\fscy80\t(0,150,\fscx100\fscy100)}HELP ME!\nDialogue: 0,0:00:24.88,0:00:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx80\fscy80\t(0,150,\fscx100\fscy100)}MY CAT IS STUCK UP IN THAT TREE!\nDialogue: 0,0:00:27.43,0:00:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx80\fscy80\t(0,150,\fscx100\fscy100)}COME HERE, KENNY!\nDialogue: 0,0:00:29.36,0:00:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx80\fscy80\t(0,150,\fscx100\fscy100)}HERE YOU GO!\nDialogue: 0,0:00:30.90,0:00:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx80\fscy80\t(0,150,\fscx100\fscy100)}THANK YOU SO MUCH!\nDialogue: 0,0:00:32.85,0:00:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx80\fscy80\t(0,150,\fscx100\fscy100)}YOU'RE EVEN BETTER THAN I IMAGINED!\nDialogue: 0,0:00:35.63,0:00:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx80\fscy80\t(0,150,\fscx100\fscy100)}I NEED TO HURRY!\nDialogue: 0,0:00:37.40,0:00:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx80\fscy80\t(0,150,\fscx100\fscy100)}I'VE TRICKED A LOT OF PEOPLE I NEED TO MAKE THINGS RIGHT.\nDialogue: 0,0:00:41.08,0:00:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx80\fscy80\t(0,150,\fscx100\fscy100)}HELP ME!\nDialogue: 0,0:00:42.52,0:00:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx80\fscy80\t(0,150,\fscx100\fscy100)}MY HOUSE IS ON FIRE!\nDialogue: 0,0:00:44.77,0:00:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx80\fscy80\t(0,150,\fscx100\fscy100)}AND MY SON IS STILL INSIDE!\nDialogue: 0,0:00:47.25,0:00:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx80\fscy80\t(0,150,\fscx100\fscy100)}I'LL SAVE YOUR SON, BACON!\nDialogue: 0,0:00:50.02,0:00:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx80\fscy80\t(0,150,\fscx100\fscy100)}YOU'RE NEW SON?\nDialogue: 0,0:00:51.67,0:00:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx80\fscy80\t(0,150,\fscx100\fscy100)}DANG IT!\nDialogue: 0,0:00:53.18,0:00:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx80\fscy80\t(0,150,\fscx100\fscy100)}I CAN ONLY DO GOOD DEEDS!\nDialogue: 0,0:00:55.45,0:00:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx80\fscy80\t(0,150,\fscx100\fscy100)}HERE YOU GO, NOOB!\nDialogue: 0,0:00:57.53,0:00:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx80\fscy80\t(0,150,\fscx100\fscy100)}THANK YOU!\nDialogue: 0,0:00:58.93,0:01:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx80\fscy80\t(0,150,\fscx100\fscy100)}I'M RUNNING OUT OF TIME!\nDialogue: 0,0:01:01.17,0:01:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx80\fscy80\t(0,150,\fscx100\fscy100)}NOXLEY!\nDialogue: 0,0:01:02.62,0:01:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx80\fscy80\t(0,150,\fscx100\fscy100)}DO YOU NEED HELP?\nDialogue: 0,0:01:04.38,0:01:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx80\fscy80\t(0,150,\fscx100\fscy100)}THANK GOODNESS SOMEONE CAME!\nDialogue: 0,0:01:06.78,0:01:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx80\fscy80\t(0,150,\fscx100\fscy100)}ACE PUT MY DOG ON THE OTHER SIDE OF THE LAVA RIVER!\nDialogue: 0,0:01:10.12,0:01:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx80\fscy80\t(0,150,\fscx100\fscy100)}OH MY GOSH!\nDialogue: 0,0:01:11.90,0:01:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx80\fscy80\t(0,150,\fscx100\fscy100)}I'LL HELP YOU!\nDialogue: 0,0:01:13.61,0:01:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx80\fscy80\t(0,150,\fscx100\fscy100)}JUST CROSS THE RIVER USING THESE BLOCKS!\nDialogue: 0,0:01:16.70,0:01:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx80\fscy80\t(0,150,\fscx100\fscy100)}I'M COMING FOR YOU, ACE!\nDialogue: 0,0:01:19.26,0:01:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx80\fscy80\t(0,150,\fscx100\fscy100)}COME HERE, DOGGY!\nDialogue: 0,0:01:21.22,0:01:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx80\fscy80\t(0,150,\fscx100\fscy100)}THANK YOU, VERITY!\nDialogue: 0,0:01:23.35,0:01:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx80\fscy80\t(0,150,\fscx100\fscy100)}I'M RUNNING OUT OF TIME, AND I STILL NEED ONE MORE GOOD DEED!\nDialogue: 0,0:01:27.47,0:01:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx80\fscy80\t(0,150,\fscx100\fscy100)}I HAVE TO FIND SOMETHING GOOD TO DO!\nDialogue: 0,0:01:30.30,0:01:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx80\fscy80\t(0,150,\fscx100\fscy100)}WELCOME BACK!\nDialogue: 0,0:01:32.15,0:01:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx80\fscy80\t(0,150,\fscx100\fscy100)}HOW WAS YOUR DAY?\nDialogue: 0,0:01:33.90,0:01:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx80\fscy80\t(0,150,\fscx100\fscy100)}UNFORTUNATELY, YOU WERE ONE GOOD DEED!\nDialogue: 0,0:01:37.05,0:01:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx80\fscy80\t(0,150,\fscx100\fscy100)}SORT OF GETTING INTO HEAVEN!\nDialogue: 0,0:01:39.55,0:01:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx80\fscy80\t(0,150,\fscx100\fscy100)}CAN YOU GIVE ME ANOTHER CHANCE?\nDialogue: 0,0:01:42.08,0:01:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx80\fscy80\t(0,150,\fscx100\fscy100)}PLEASE!\nDialogue: 0,0:01:43.46,0:01:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx80\fscy80\t(0,150,\fscx100\fscy100)}I'LL GIVE YOU THIS SWORD WITH AMAZING POWERS!\nDialogue: 0,0:01:47.01,0:01:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx80\fscy80\t(0,150,\fscx100\fscy100)}DOES HE DESERVE ANOTHER CHANCE?\nDialogue: 0,0:01:49.58,0:01:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx80\fscy80\t(0,150,\fscx100\fscy100)}THANKS SO!\nDialogue: 0,0:01:51.06,0:01:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx80\fscy80\t(0,150,\fscx100\fscy100)}LEAVE A LIKE!\n